verse.lines:
{lang-eng}O Jesus, our Jesus, with Thee we are blest—
Our Life, our Enjoyment, our Peace and our Rest:
Thy name be our theme, and Thy love be our song;
Thy love has inspired both our heart and our tongue!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}We love Thee, we love Thee, we love Thee, O Lord.
We love Thee, our Jesus, we love Thee, our God!
We love Thee, we love Thee, and that Thou dost know;
As we’re in Thy presence, love for Thee will grow!{/lang-eng}
